text: Park Mi-jeong (born 3 March 1968) is a South Korean rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
